Participant datagridClickHandler Participant gui Participant datagrid Participant maptips
Note over datagridClickHandler: User clicks
details link datagridClickHandler->gui:gui.subpanel_open
Note over gui:Populates and
opens panel gui->featureHighlighter:featurehighlighter.hightlight_show Note over featureHighlighter: Highlights feature on the map featureHighlighter->maptips:maptips.show_interactive Note over maptips: Shows interactive maptip Note over maptips:Checks if maptip
 is covered by slide panel
Note over maptips:CASE 1: maptip is not covered maptips->featureClickHandler:maptip.extent_change("scroll": true) featureClickHandler->datagrid:datagrid.highlightrow_show("scroll": true) Note right of datagrid:Scrolls to and 
 highlights selected row
Note over maptips:CASE 2: maptip is covered maptips-->>map:map.center_at maptips-->>featureClickHandler:maptip.extent_change("scroll": false) featureClickHandler-->>datagrid:datagrid.highlightrow_show("scroll": false) Note over datagrid:Remebers row to
highlight later;
does not scroll
Note over map: Map finishes 
 updating map-->>bootstrapper:map.update_end map-->>featureHighlighter:map.zoom_end 
 map.pan_end Note over featureHighlighter:Calculates new maptip offset featureHighlighter-->>maptips:maptips.reposition_interactive Note over maptips: Repositions maptip
bootstrapper-->>datagrid:datagrid.apply_extent_filter Note right of datagrid:Scrolls to and 
 highlights selected row
